  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research settings to predict hemolysis in centrifugal blood pump configurations. The CFD hemolysis model targets the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry under ventricular assist device operating conditions. All thirteen ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated against the model risk level, and the overall assessment concludes that sufficient credibility evidence has been assembled to support the intended regulatory submission. This package conforms to the Minimal profile; detailed context-of-use scope is documented separately in the project technical file and is not reproduced here.",
