      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification using manufactured solutions required for all active transport equations.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy tests were conducted for the momentum equations; the scalar hemolysis transport equation was not independently verified via manufactured solution."
    },
