      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI with three systematically refined grids; GCI below 5% on hemolysis index QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-level grid refinement study performed; GCI on hemolysis index is 8.2%, exceeding the 5% threshold. Spatial discretization error is quantified but not sufficiently controlled."
    },
    {
