      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions must match simulation inlet/outlet conditions within measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Flow rate, inlet pressure, and fluid temperature were matched to experimental conditions within stated measurement uncertainty bands. This factor meets the required level."
    },
