      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric-based comparison (e.g., E_rms, validation uncertainty) with statistical characterization of experimental scatter.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index predictions are within 18% of experimental means; however, validation uncertainty analysis does not fully account for inter-laboratory variability in the reference dataset."
